    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors were assessed. Achieved levels fall below required levels for several factors, but the assessment team determined that the aggregate evidence is sufficient to support the intended use decision for the VAD hemolysis prediction. Validation results across five operating points demonstrate acceptable agreement with experimental data. The assessment is accepted subject to the documented factor gaps.",
